   <title>
    銅鑼灣總統戲院明日結業 有市民感可惜：俾巨輪碌死咗
   </title>
   <link>
    https://www.inmediahk.net/node/%E7%94%9F%E6%B4%BB/%E9%8A%85%E9%91%BC%E7%81%A3%E7%B8%BD%E7%B5%B1%E6%88%B2%E9%99%A2%E6%98%8E%E6%97%A5%E7%B5%90%E6%A5%AD-%E6%9C%89%E5%B8%82%E6%B0%91%E6%84%9F%E5%8F%AF%E6%83%9C%EF%BC%9A%E4%BF%BE%E5%B7%A8%E8%BC%AA%E7%A2%8C%E6%AD%BB%E5%92%97
