    <![CDATA[<div class="field field-name-taxonomy-vocabulary-18 field-type-taxonomy-term-reference field-label-above"><div class="field-label">內容: </div><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even"><a href="/lifestyle">生活</a></div></div></div><div class="field field-name-field-image field-type-image field-label-hidden"><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even"><img src="https://images.weserv.nl/?n=-1&url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Ffiles%2Fcolumn_images%2F20240429_1540960-01.jpg" width="940" height="492" alt="" /></div></div></div><div class="field field-name-taxonomy-vocabulary-19 field-type-taxonomy-term-reference field-label-above"><div class="field-label">自由標籤: </div><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even"><a href="/taxonomy/term/528473">獨媒報導</a></div><div class="field-item odd"><a href="/taxonomy/term/539252">總統戲院</a></div><div class="field-item even"><a href="/taxonomy/term/503119">銅鑼灣</a></div><div class="field-item odd"><a href="/taxonomy/term/517921">戲院</a></div><div class="field-item even"><a href="/taxonomy/term/500211">電影</a></div><div class="field-item odd"><a href="/taxonomy/term/539253">新寶院線</a></div></div></div><div class="field field-name-body field-type-text-with-summary field-label-hidden"><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even"><p><font color="red">（獨媒報導）</font>繼新蒲崗嘉禾啟德戲院於「全港戲院日」翌日結業後，本月內再有戲院結業。新寶院線前日（27日）在社交平台宣布，總統戲院將於明日（4月30日）光榮結業，感謝觀眾支持。有市民得悉戲院結業特意前來送別，認為現時入場看電影人數較以往少，氣氛稍遜，對於戲院結業則感可惜：「無辦法啦，趨勢嚟架嘛」、「俾巨輪碌死咗。」</p>
<p>位於銅鑼灣謝斐道的總統戲院，於1966年10月26日正式開業，迄今有約58年歷史。戲院原有兩層共1248個座位，不過2001年改建成迷你戲院後，座位減至餘下428個。</p>
<p><a data-flickr-embed="true" href="https://www.flickr.com/gp/inmediahk/Z53a1955E8" title="無標題"><img src="https://images.weserv.nl/?n=-1&url=https%3A%2F%2Flive.staticflickr.com%2F65535%2F53686143901_bfcaa91e3c_b.jpg" width="1024" alt="無標題" /></a></p>
<p><a data-flickr-embed="true" href="https://www.flickr.com/gp/inmediahk/Ztd9QG6g0X" title="無標題"><img src="https://images.weserv.nl/?n=-1&url=https%3A%2F%2Flive.staticflickr.com%2F65535%2F53686509214_b1566141f0_b.jpg" width="1024" alt="無標題" /></a></p>
<p><a data-flickr-embed="true" href="https://www.flickr.com/gp/inmediahk/jM6B8fc37L" title="無標題"><img src="https://images.weserv.nl/?n=-1&url=https%3A%2F%2Flive.staticflickr.com%2F65535%2F53686368103_d8f6bf68cd_b.jpg" width="1024" alt="無標題" /></a></p>
<p><a data-flickr-embed="true" href="https://www.flickr.com/gp/inmediahk/s62grccR0S" title="無標題"><img src="https://images.weserv.nl/?n=-1&url=https%3A%2F%2Flive.staticflickr.com%2F65535%2F53686144236_7f3dfe0384_b.jpg" width="1024" alt="無標題" /></a></p>
<p>新寶院線前日（27日）在社交平台宣布，銅鑼灣總統戲院將於周二（30日）光榮結業，感謝觀眾支持，不過文中就未有交代結業原因。總統戲院告別後，新寶院線就只餘兩間戲院，分別為旺角新寶戲院和屯門凱都戲院。</p>
<p>《獨媒》記者今早11時（29日）到戲院視察，現場未見有張貼結業告示。今早不少市民特意到場購票看電影以及手持戲票拍照留念，亦有人向記者表示是首次到總統戲院看戲。</p>
<p><a data-flickr-embed="true" href="https://www.flickr.com/gp/inmediahk/m09Bz4G3E0" title="無標題"><img src="https://images.weserv.nl/?n=-1&url=https%3A%2F%2Flive.staticflickr.com%2F65535%2F53686368558_c2041315d7_b.jpg" width="1024" alt="無標題" /></a></p>
<p><a data-flickr-embed="true" href="https://www.flickr.com/gp/inmediahk/9MkmmwU18r" title="無標題"><img src="https://images.weserv.nl/?n=-1&url=https%3A%2F%2Flive.staticflickr.com%2F65535%2F53686144191_c4fef531c6_b.jpg" width="1024" alt="無標題" /></a></p>
<p><a data-flickr-embed="true" href="https://www.flickr.com/gp/inmediahk/w2z80mm1C6" title="無標題"><img src="https://images.weserv.nl/?n=-1&url=https%3A%2F%2Flive.staticflickr.com%2F65535%2F53686370203_f133fab8a9_b.jpg" width="1024" alt="無標題" /></a></p>
<p><strong>有市民認為戲院結業在所難免：俾巨輪碌死咗</strong></p>
<p>已退休的陳先生今日特意偕妻到場送別，形容自己由「10歲細路睇到宜家」。他認為現時入戲院看電影人數較以往少，氣氛較為遜色，僅得「小貓幾隻」。而且戲院結業亦在所難免：「咁少人（入場）自然會淘汰，唔係唔支持吖，太多媒體啦宜家，以前想睇戲就入戲院囉，電視都無乜轉載，要睇戲就入戲院。」被問到戲院結業會否感到可惜，陳先生說：「無辦法啦，趨勢嚟架嘛」、「俾巨輪碌死咗。」</p>
<p><a data-flickr-embed="true" href="https://www.flickr.com/gp/inmediahk/j721V97p36" title="陳先生與太太"><img src="https://images.weserv.nl/?n=-1&url=https%3A%2F%2Flive.staticflickr.com%2F65535%2F53685275642_fe64b7721e_b.jpg" width="1024" alt="陳先生與太太" /></a><br /><em>陳先生與太太</em></p>
<p><a data-flickr-embed="true" href="https://www.flickr.com/gp/inmediahk/3k21uJF8Rn" title="無標題"><img src="https://images.weserv.nl/?n=-1&url=https%3A%2F%2Flive.staticflickr.com%2F65535%2F53686369133_07ccf0f764_b.jpg" width="1024" alt="無標題" /></a></p>
<p><strong>市民懷緬兒時首次看戲 認為戲院結業對電影業影響不大</strong></p>
<p>另一位陳先生得悉戲院明日結業，同樣特意前來「懷緬一下」。他憶述自己四十多年前首次在總統大戲院看電影，認為當時感受較深刻：「大戲院感覺好多人睇戲、好開心」、「（當時）通常都做金公主院線嘅港產片，最佳拍檔嗰啲，睇完好開心、好熱鬧。」不過，自從總統戲院改建迷你戲院後便減少入場次數。</p>
<p><a data-flickr-embed="true" href="https://www.flickr.com/gp/inmediahk/A96a7264Ze" title="陳先生"><img src="https://images.weserv.nl/?n=-1&url=https%3A%2F%2Flive.staticflickr.com%2F65535%2F53685273237_c36ece06a0_b.jpg" width="1024" alt="陳先生" /></a><br /><em>陳先生</em></p>
<p>本月內先後有不同戲院結業，陳先生認為，總統戲院結業對電影業影響不大：「以依個市道嚟講，其實少咗呢間係咪咁真係大影響呢？咁又唔係嘅，都係一種感情姐。」</p>
<p><a data-flickr-embed="true" href="https://www.flickr.com/gp/inmediahk/L9V5sw6Tgn" title="無標題"><img src="https://images.weserv.nl/?n=-1&url=https%3A%2F%2Flive.staticflickr.com%2F65535%2F53686370178_ca333ea73b_b.jpg" width="1024" alt="無標題" /></a></p>
<p><a data-flickr-embed="true" href="https://www.flickr.com/gp/inmediahk/q2T11w6KjE" title="無標題"><img src="https://images.weserv.nl/?n=-1&url=https%3A%2F%2Flive.staticflickr.com%2F65535%2F53686147641_bbe8e71cc8_b.jpg" width="1024" alt="無標題" /></a></p>
<p><a data-flickr-embed="true" href="https://www.flickr.com/gp/inmediahk/48uhDbNtVd" title="無標題"><img src="https://images.weserv.nl/?n=-1&url=https%3A%2F%2Flive.staticflickr.com%2F65535%2F53685274362_9b0b959b35_b.jpg" width="1024" alt="無標題" /></a></p>
</div></div></div>]]>
